	dprr:hasNoteText "Legatus pro praetore in Asia under Lucullus (CIL 12.2.743-ILS 37). See 74, Legates." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/4443> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #4443" ;
